03:00.583 --> 03:02.041
When's it over, Crick?

03:02.166 --> 03:06.416
Well, uh, Mr. Sun has been
on holiday for a long time,

03:06.541 --> 03:09.750
but I crickto-calculate

03:09.875 --> 03:13.916
that he is due to appear exactly...

03:14.041 --> 03:15.333
