it means...

16:29.875 --> 16:31.125
It...

16:32.208 --> 16:33.583
It means, "Ouch."

16:33.708 --> 16:36.000
Wow, you sure are clever.

16:36.125 --> 16:38.541
Oh, well. Thank you.

16:38.666 --> 16:39.875
